data.text: @ewnupdates As a mother of two kids I have battled alot with my financial state to the point of begging from friends just to survive,until I started Bitcoin trading with the help of @_AMBREYMARCUS1 I made a successful withdrawal of R 200,000 with the help of @_ambreymarcus1.
@ewnupdates More like lack of intelligence inhibiting their studies.

@ewnupdates Being the head of the home isn't easy, you are expected to provide for the home, I lost my job during the pandemic and relied on the little money I had,things were hard until I met @_ambreymarcus1 and started Bitcoin trading, I earned  R150,000 in 3 weeks thanks @_ambreymarcus1.
@ewnupdates Not sure how a vaccine requirement that is free of charge  is an economic hardship to learners. Do journalists even engage with the story and try to get basic info before printing rubbish

@ewnupdates I know we all probably must have heard about Bitcoin but don't know how it works, I tried it in a week ago by a man who recommended me to @Leticia_thomas5 on Twitter She guides me through and i made a return of R15500 after a week of trading, connect with her

@ewnupdates Behind every successful person there's always a helper @Charlesmike109 is the person behind my success story she helped me earn R400,000.  thanks for restoring my hope once again  @Charlesmike109
